folder: Monroe Street & Gouverneur Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Monroe Street, east across Gouverneur Street, showing the demolition for the government sponsered public housing project, the USHA "Vladeck Houses". The cleared blockfront in the foreground is the narrow frontage from Gouverneur to Scammel Street's.
June 23, 1939
No's. 1-2-3
P. L. SPERR
